{"tid":459442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係唔想捐血，不過你班姑娘......","createTime":"2017-11-05T17:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T06:55:16.000Z","uid":84013,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2d11d101a3dd1cd78f484fc2bc586e257cab64","tid":459442,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"次撚次捐血都好似想榨乾榨盡我咁<br />\n你老母血庫唔夠血我都已經黎捐啦<br />\n仆你個街每一次都問捐多D好唔好<br />\n一係直接問都唔問話今次捐多D<br />\n屌你老味抽到隻手又乾又痺D血唔出<br />\n同姑娘講又詐諦唔知叫我喐下隻手就算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我都想捐多D呀，不過可唔可以唔好下下榨乾榨盡</span><br />\n<br />\n利申:一年2~3次,未來應該不了"},{"pid":"c79726d9563f635ed88f18656d780d695ff2f27f","tid":459442,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:47:25.000Z","msg":"肉醬多利亞"},{"pid":"aa0652188d4c43d6804b257902cb9e952e06eaad","tid":459442,"uid":127962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"屌你講到吸血鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59de5f38b20a91c63f2d4046ea507c544dbdf1dc","tid":459442,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"一次都未捐過亦無呢個打算"},{"pid":"0dc9e77b4761e1a16a90c32c0d2c36441695e92b","tid":459442,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"捐完會唔會面青口唇白？"},{"pid":"8195dfbf83e328271117b71b4d62aaa4c7598d08","tid":459442,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T18:18:35.000Z","msg":"聽講香港d血會拎去大陸用"},{"pid":"70d50aca0b61b6812b0c6920718a350b5ee5c12b","tid":459442,"uid":155534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講香港d血會拎去大陸用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對於港血運回內地的說法，紅十字會今日嚴正澄清，指不時收到相關查詢，已多次作出澄清以正視聽。發言人重申<strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">中心多年來一直沒有向香港以外地區提供血液予病人使用，所有收集回來的血液均是供應予本地所有醫院，為病人作臨床輸血治療。</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n中心重申，若本港病人需尋稀有血型血液，中心會協助在海外尋找合適血液作輸血治療；但基於人道精神考慮，若港血供應充足甚至有餘額，本港病人不需用上所有血液時或會作個別例外考慮，將剩餘血液幫助本港以外的病人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160710/s00001/1468158096180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160710%2Fs00001%2F1468158096180&d=KUqi25VSXYs8MR38YhxzY49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=adec092c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160710%2Fs00001%2F1468158096180&h=8202716c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160710/s00001/1468158096180</a><br />\n<br />\n其實都出哂新聞話d血唔係俾大陸人用&hellip;"}]}